OL,3,CMan who attacked police during
OL,4,Cdisorder admits riot charge
OL,6,FA man who was filmed kicking out at
OL,7,Fpolice during widespread disorder in
OL,8,FSunderland has admitted a charge of
OL,9,Friot.
OL,11,FJohn Kirtley, of Rutherglen Road in
OL,12,Fthe city, appeared at Newcastle Crown
OL,13,FCourt where he pleaded guilty to the
OL,14,Foffence he committed on 2 August.
OL,16,FHe had previously admitted a charge of
OL,17,Fviolent disorder, but that was
OL,18,Fupgraded to the more serious offence
OL,19,Fof riot.
