OL,3,CMan who attacked police during
OL,4,Cdisorder admits riot charge
OL,6,FKirtley found out on Monday (2
OL,7,FDecember) that an application to have
OL,8,Fthe riot charge thrown out, due to
OL,9,Fwhat his legal team claimed was an
OL,10,Fabuse of process, had failed.
OL,12,FJudge Julie Clemitson said he would be
OL,13,Fsentenced on 31 January.
OL,15,FImages released after the case by
OL,16,FNorthumbria Police showed Kirtley, at
OL,17,Ftimes topless and waving an England
OL,18,Fflag around, pushing a shopping
OL,19,Ftrolley towards police lines and
OL,20,Fkicking out at officers in riot gear.
